- Extract specific characters from text.
- Replace unwanted text with new values.
- Count characters in a text string.
- Convert text to uppercase, lowercase, or proper case.

## Reflection
Reviewing these functions helped reinforce my understanding of text manipulation in Excel. These skills are essential for data cleaning and preparation, which are important steps in the data analysis process.

